,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## Summary\n\nUpgrade `@joshuafolkken/kit` from v0.132.0 to v0.167.0 and apply the accompanying config/workflow improvements synced from the kit.\n\n## Changes\n\n- **Kit upgrade**: `@joshuafolkken/kit` 0.132.0 → 0.167.0 (pnpm-lock.yaml updated)\n- **auto-tag.yml**: Refactored trigger from `push` path-filter to `repository_dispatch` event — eliminates CI polling loop inside auto-tag\n- **ci.yml**: Added `notify-auto-tag` job that dispatches the event after all checks pass; improved per-job `permissions` scoping; upgraded `pnpm/action-setup` to v6.0.5; fixed E2E detect to require both `playwright.config.ts` AND an actual `.e2e.ts` file; removed redundant `pnpm build` step in E2E job\n- **sonar-cube.yml → sonar-qube.yml**: Renamed to correct the typo\n- **playwright.config.ts**: Introduced `EnvConfig` type and `web_server_config` object; adjusted timeouts; dev mode uses `pnpm dev` with `reuseExistingServer`\n- **pnpm-workspace.yaml**: Migrated `onlyBuiltDependencies` → `allowBuilds` (new pnpm field)\n- **package.json**: Added `devEngines` pinning pnpm ≥ 11; updated `postinstall` to run `fix-gh-packages.ts`\n- **.npmrc**: Added `confirmModulesPurge=false`\n- **sonar-project.properties**: Fixed CPD exclusions to include `*.e2e.ts`\n- **CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md / GEMINI.md**: Added `devEngines` guard rule, recovery-after-failed-push note, and config-file-update-check section\n\n## Testing\n\nNon-runtime changes only — manual verification: lint, tsc, cspell, unit tests.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/mnemecha/issues/237/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/mnemecha/issues/237/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owasp-noir/noir/issues/1184","repository_url":"https://api.git