s_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joshuafolkken/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joshuafolkken/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joshuafolkken/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":10785180348,"node_id":"LA_kwDOQSaIp88AAAACgtjKvA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/labels/in-progress","name":"in-progress","color":"0075ca","default":false,"description":"Currently being worked on"}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2026-05-15T04:17:51Z","updated_at":"2026-05-15T04:46:12Z","closed_at":"2026-05-15T04:46:10Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"OWNER","active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## Background\n\nGitHub Dependabot raised 3 open medium-severity alerts against `svelte` in this repo:\n\n- **Alert #46** — Svelte: SSR XSS via Insecure Promise Serialization in hydratable (vulnerable: `>= 5.46.0, <= 5.55.6`)\n- **Alert #47** — Svelte SSR vulnerable to cross-site scripting via spread attributes (vulnerable: `<= 5.55.6`)\n- **Alert #48** — Svelte Vulnerable to XSS via DOM Clobbering of Internal Framework State (vulnerable: `<= 5.55.6`)\n\nAll three are fixed in svelte 5.55.7.\n\n## Expected Result\n\n- `svelte` direct dep bumped to `^5.55.7`\n- Transitive resolutions also forced to `>=5.55.7` via a `pnpm.overrides` entry (so any dep pulling svelte through resolves the security fix)\n- `devalue` (used by SvelteKit for SSR serialization, implicated in alert #46) pinned to `^5.8.1`\n- `pnpm.overrides` tidied: drop entries that are no longer needed (`undici`, `drizzle-orm`, `@sveltejs/kit`, `uuid`) and simplify range formats for `esbuild` / `cookie`\n- `packageManager` pnpm patch bump: 11.1.1 → 11.1.2\n- All Dependabot alerts close; CI green\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `svelte` resolved version `>= 5.55.7` everywhere in the lockfile\n- [ ] `devalue` resolved version `>= 5.8.1`\n- [ ] `pnpm.overrides` reflects the refactor; no regressions on dropped overrides\n- [ ] `pnpm install` succeeds with no peer-dep errors\n- [ ] Existing unit (`pnpm josh test:unit`) + E2E (`pnpm josh test`) suites pass\n- [ ] Dependabot alerts #46, #47, #48 auto-close after merge","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/592/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/592/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/600","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/600/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/600/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/600/events","html_url":"https://github.com/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/600","id":4460496353,"node_id":"I_kwDOQSaIp88AAAABCd3F4Q","number":600,"title":"Bump @joshuafolkken/kit to 0.173.0","user":{"login":"joshuafolkken","id":168330964,"node_id":"U_kgDOCgiG1A","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/168330964?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/joshuafolkken","html_url":"https://github.com/joshuafolkken","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joshuafolkken/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joshuafolkken/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joshuafolkken/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.git